style="font-family:Verdana;">80%</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">。深入推进脱贫攻坚，</span><span
style="font-family:Verdana;">31</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">个经济薄弱村和</span><span
style="font-family:Verdana;">9400</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">余户贫困人口成功脱贫，</span><span
